The paper proposes a novel algorithm for video quality adaptation in HTTP Adaptive Streaming (HAS) in mobile networks. This involves machine learning techniques and optimization algorithms, which are commonly found in the sub-categories of Multimedia (cs.MM), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Information Theory (cs.IT), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
